I may revoke my express consent at any time; I have also been informed that, in accordance with the Regulation on Commercial Electronic Messages, I must give my consent to the sending of e-mails and SMS messages to customers during the online shopping process, and that I may revoke my consent at any time in accordance with the right to refuse.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIn this context, I expressly consent to the processing, collection and storage of my personal data, consisting of my name, surname, telephone number and e-mail address, for the purposes and under the conditions set out above. I also consent to the sending of e-mails and SMS messages to me.','EXPLICIT CONSENT','','inherit','closed','closed','','723-revision-v1','','','2024-03-25 16:58:45','2024-03-25 13:58:45','',723,'http://solino.local/?p=761',0,'revision','',0);
